__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  GetPlantsResponseItem:
    properties:
      id: optional<integer>
      name: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    getPlants:
      path: /plants
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Get plants (inherits global ApiKeyAuth)
      response:
        docs: List of plants
        type: list<GetPlantsResponseItem>
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              - id: 1
                name: name
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Security Global Inheritance Test
environments:
  Default: https://api.example.com/v1
default-environment: Default
auth-schemes:
  ApiKeyAuth:
    header: x-api-key
    name: apiKey
    type: string
auth: ApiKeyAuth
